Class Address

java.lang.Object
  hoipolloi.Address

public class Address
extends java.lang.Object

An Address datatype consisting of Label, Address Line 1, 2, and 3, City, State, Zip, Country, District and Type (Residential, Billing, Mailing etc).

Method Detail

areRequiredPartsFilled

public boolean areRequiredPartsFilled()
Checks if all the required parts of this Address are filled. The minimum required parts are: Type, Line 1, City, State, Zip and Country. The rest of the parts are optional.

Returns:
True if all the required parts are filled, otherwise false.
